Products

Fabric & Yarns

At our company we specialize in providing high-quality row fabrics to meet the diverse needs of our customers. Our extensive collection of fabrics includes:

Cotton

100% Cotton.

Half Panama

Half Panama a woven textile, manufactured with two warp yarns over each weft.

Pique

Pique is a durable cotton knit fabric covered with a tiny, textured pattern.

Flannel

Flannel is a loosely woven fabric known for being soft and warm.

Cretonne

Cretonne is a 100% cotton fabric that is 121gsm.

Ranforce

Ranforce fabric is a type of fabric that is made from 100% cotton.
